data.description:
Welcome home to this elegant custom built Sprawling Contemporary ranch! Giving you the benefits of one-floor living, while also featuring multiple living areas, ample storage, and High-end finishes. Sitting on over a 3 acre rear lot, that fronts Directly with Scoville Reservoir giving you stunning views and access of the water. This home features 6 Bedrooms and 6 Full bathrooms plus an additional 2 Guest bathrooms. The main level of the home features your grand entryway with vaulted ceilings, your spacious all-white modern eat-in kitchen, Your formal living room and Dinning room separated by a custom stone chimney. The main level also gives you access to your indoor swimming pool and hot tub, as well as your Master suite, featuring stunning views, a gas fireplace, expansive walk-in closet, and your Master bathroom with dual sinks, Jacuzzi tub, and tiled shower. This home has everything you Want and Need and has been meticulously maintained. Schedule your private tour today, and make this 1 of a kind home yours!

2 hours to New York City
25 Min to Hartford, CT
20 Min to ESPN Headquarters in Bristol, CT
2 Hrs to Boston, MA

Possible owner financing
